cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new architecture for deep neural networks that enhances parameter efficiency through collective tensor factorization. This work is related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL) as it proposes a new architecture for deep neural networks that can be applied to various tasks such as image classification and natural language processing.
